page1.title: About Me
page1.content: Hi, I’m Tom Whelan, a data scientist from the UK. I created this page as a central point of reference for blog posts about various projects I have worked on. If you’re looking for my series teaching machine learning with Python through a fantasy football lens, you can find it at fantasyfutopia.com. . Feel free to get in touch with me on Twitter (@tom_whelan) or via email (tom.whelan@hotmail.co.uk). .
